data.description: Welcome to 8780 CR 521 in the coveted Pine River Valley.  This wonderful property is located less than a mile from downtown Bayfield and a short 25 minute drive to downtown Durango.  The 4626 SF home is ideally situated on the 12.73 acre parcel.  The home has been perfectly situated on the parcel providing outstanding views of the La Plata Mountains and the Pine River Valley to the west and the HD Mountains to the east. The home which was built in 2015 features 5 bedrooms and 4 ½ baths on two levels. The main level features an inviting living room leading to the spacious kitchen with island seating and plenty of room for a large dining room table.  The Home includes a split floor plan with the primary suite situated on the south end of the home.  The ensuite bathroom has duel vanities, a soaking tub and walk-in shower and a large walk-in closet.  The north end of the home has two additional guest bedrooms, a full bathroom, laundry room and office or den.  The huge deck off of the kitchen is a great place to take in the views and hear the elk bugling in the valley below.  Downstairs features a second living area with ample room for games.  The south end of the walk-out basement has two additional bedrooms. The north end has two additional rooms for in home gym, office or storage!  Outside the pride of ownership is evident.  The property has an inground sprinkler system designed to run off the irrigation water that conveys with the property providing for green grass and great flower beds.  The in-ground trampoline will be a sure hit  for the kids.  Additionally the pasture has been completely fenced for horse or cows and is irrigated via the Schroder Ditch and the Pine River Irrigation District.  A loafing shed was recently added for livestock and the chicken coop will stay with the property! There are also frost free hydrants throughout the property and ample level space to park horse trailers, campers or equipment.  In this low inventory market, this thoroughly and thoughtfully well-maintained property has it all… schedule your showing today!
